<h3><br />Questions and comments form</h3>
<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>
<p><strong><br />Who should I address my query to?</strong></p>
<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>
<ul type="disc">
<li>The&nbsp;Regjeringen.no editors answer questions relating to the services provided by Regjeringen.no: functions, errors, how to find information on Regjeringen.no, etc. </li>
<li>The Office of the Prime Minister and the ministries answer questions relating to their own pages on Regjeringen.no.</li>
</ul>
<p><br />If you need help in finding your way around the public administration or in finding publicly available information, you may contact <a href="http://www.norway.no/" target="ext">Norway.no</a>, e-mail <img id='Eoi_2' class='obfimg' src='/upload/system/emailimages/a788eb9300d23b1db343284a45f4ea5e.png' alt='' /><script type="text/javascript" id="Eos_2"><!--
